OL,3,CHip-hop pioneer Afrika Bambaataa dies
OL,4,Caged 68
OL,6,FHip-hop pioneer Afrika Bambaataa, who
OL,7,Finspired a generation of artists but
OL,8,Fwas later overshadowed by sexual abuse
OL,9,Fallegations, has died aged 68.
OL,11,FBambaataa's lawyer said he died from
OL,12,Fprostate cancer in Pennsylvania on
OL,13,FThursday.
OL,15,FHis sudden death was met with an
OL,16,Foutpouring of condolences from
OL,17,Ffriends, family, and fans across the
OL,18,Fworld, who paid tribute to his impact
OL,19,Fon hip-hop.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
