OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775823080
OL,3,CHip-hop pioneer Afrika Bambaataa dies
OL,4,Caged 68
OL,6,FBut others have said that his impact
OL,7,Fwas overshadowed in recent years after
OL,8,Fnumerous men who knew Bambaataa when
OL,9,Fthey were boys accused him of sexual
OL,10,Fabuse.
OL,12,FThe rapper and producer was best known
OL,13,Ffor breakthrough tracks like 1982's
OL,14,FPlanet Rock and for founding the
OL,15,FUniversal Zulu Nation art collective.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
