OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775823080
OL,3,CHip-hop pioneer Afrika Bambaataa dies
OL,4,Caged 68
OL,6,F"Hip-Hop will never be the same
OL,7,Fwithout him - but everything hip-hop
OL,8,Fis today, it is because of him. His
OL,9,Fspirit lives in every beat, every
OL,10,Fcypher and every corner of this globe
OL,11,Fhe touched," his talent agency, Naf
OL,12,FManagement Entertainment, wrote in a
OL,13,Fstatement.
OL,15,FBambaataa was born Lance Taylor in
OL,16,F1957 in the South Bronx of New York
OL,17,FCity during an age when the area was
OL,18,Fsuffering from intense economic
OL,19,Fdecline after years of intense
OL,20,Fsegregation and neglect from officials.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
