OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775823080
OL,3,CHip-hop pioneer Afrika Bambaataa dies
OL,4,Caged 68
OL,6,FHe had Jamaican and Barbadian
OL,7,Fheritage, and he was raised in a low-
OL,8,Fincome public housing complex by his
OL,9,Fmother.
OL,11,FHe was exposed to music at an early
OL,12,Fage through his mother's vinyl record
OL,13,Fcollection. He began hosting parties
OL,14,Fin the 1970s and made a name for
OL,15,Fhimself by repurposing and remixing
OL,16,Fold hits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
