OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775823080
OL,3,CHip-hop pioneer Afrika Bambaataa dies
OL,4,Caged 68
OL,6,FIn 2016, Bronx political activist and
OL,7,Fformer music industry executive Ronald
OL,8,FSavage accused Bambaataa of abusing
OL,9,Fhim in 1980, when he was a young teen.
OL,11,F"I was scared, but at the same time I
OL,12,Fwas like, 'This is Afrika Bambaataa,'"
OL,13,FSavage said in 2016. At the time, he
OL,14,Frecalled, in detail, that encounter
OL,15,Fand four others that he said followed.
OL,17,FBambaataa vehemently denied the
OL,18,Fallegations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
