PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775823080
OL,3,CHip-hop pioneer Afrika Bambaataa dies
OL,4,Caged 68
OL,6,FAfter Savage went public with his
OL,7,Fclaims, numerous other men came
OL,8,Fforward to share similar experiences
OL,9,Fabout Bambaataa.
OL,11,FIn June 2016, the Universal Zulu
OL,12,FNation released a public letter
OL,13,Fapologising to "the survivors of
OL,14,Fapparent sexual molestation by
OL,15,FBambaataa" saying that some members of
OL,16,Fthe group knew about the abuse but
OL,17,F"chose not to disclose" it.
OL,26,@uD@POUyD@AOUyD@WO]
